Package gw.api.print

Class AbstractCCPrintAction

java.lang.Object
gw.api.print.PrintAction
gw.api.print.AbstractCCPrintAction
Direct Known Subclasses:
CustomPrintAction, PrintOutAction
public abstract class AbstractCCPrintAction extends PrintAction
Classification of print actions that are supported only in CC. A special CC-specific print context factory is associated with such print actions, which allows application-specific FOP instructions to be accessed.
